NOTE: I'm using v0.20.3.0-beta. However, the issue seems to still exist in v0.24.0, since I found the following issue in the v24 source as well. In the following analysis, I'll be talking about the v24 (latest stable) source code, downloaded from the website's Releases section.

The cause seems to be that env.deviceHeight is not the device height but rather the app container height instead. Weex seems to be doing the following to get the display height: 

``` 
Resources.getSystem().getDisplayMetrics().heightPixels
```

However, this the height minus the navigation and status bars. 
It might be a good idea to edit this so it works as in iOS. To get the actual device height, you need to call:

```
WindowManager wm = (WindowManager) thisActivity.getSystemService(Context.WINDOW_SERVICE);
Display display = wm.getDefaultDisplay();
Point size = new Point();
display.getRealSize(size); // API > 17
// do something with size.y
```

I found it in the following files. Once I have more time I'll try to patch it and see if it breaks anything. I'm quite new to contributing to open source projects.

> apache/taobao/weex/WXSDKEngine.java:192:    registerCoreEnv("screen_height_pixels", String.valueOf(resources.getDisplayMetrics().heightPixels));
> apache/taobao/weex/utils/WXViewUtils.java:184:      mScreenHeight =cxt.getResources().getDisplayMetrics().heightPixels;

- Answer1、2: collectIdTask代码如下：

`class collectIdTask extends AsyncTask<Integer, Integer, String> {
            @Override
            protected void onPreExecute() {
                super.onPreExecute();
            }
            @Override
            protected String doInBackground(Integer... params) {
                try {
                    collectIDMap();
                    Thread.sleep(1000);
                }catch (Exception e) {}
                return "执行完毕";
            }
            @Override
            protected void onProgressUpdate(Integer... progress) {
                super.onProgressUpdate(progress);
            }
            @Override
            protected void onPostExecute(String result) {
                mWXHandler.sendEmptyMessage(1);
                //Log.d("main", "== sendMessage ==");
                super.onPostExecute(result);
            }
        }`

- Answer3: R.id.container_test_id 是在Activity的根结点上增加的一个FrameLayout，用于存储当前页面所有testId与nativeId的映射关系

- Answer4: mIDMap是一个全局对象，用于存储Activity中testId和nativeId的映射关系，会在每次发现新的testId时将最新的映射关系写到container_test_id的ContentDescription中。代码如下：
`container.setContentDescription(JSON.toJSONString(mIDMap));`
